{"tid":906200,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有心事入嚟擺低 無心事入嚟吹水 (372)","createTime":"2018-11-17T18:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T02:44:19.000Z","uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4de67c34207a1d95a1ef30f93bcb0138db92d20","tid":906200,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:25:55.000Z","msg":"唔小心三百七十二咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續有心事入嚟擺低 無心事入嚟吹水<br />\n絕非小圈子 有心事就算見到吹緊水都唔使怕羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲比既意見會比較直擊 大家唔好嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有啲巴絲講野好低b 因為都係無聊野傾到冇野傾先講低b嘢<br />\n所以好歡迎新話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲會po啲好黑既嘢<br />\n又有時候會無啦啦變左成人台<br />\n如果你handle唔到可以唔理佢地<br />\nhandle唔到都無辦法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望多啲人討論歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋遷就唔識英文同日文嘅巴絲 唔該<br />\n但係希望大家唔好歌詞/藝人相洗版 咁會嚇親有心事既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果見到有啲reply覺得唔係太舒服 請體諒呢個po大多都係有心事有情緒既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋大家都注意返 對啲有心事有情緒既巴絲 唔好講啲刺激性攻擊性既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請1001嘅巴絲開po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ecb7d79643a943b17851a18d98b3de2f11cf92","tid":906200,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:29:20.000Z","msg":"好似冇人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011af87b0100bb7e09fe5d6d2e8dc563aa87cf02","tid":906200,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:30:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0dd8a4ed3d4509af5a15432b0b973e630585d42","tid":906200,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"011af87b0100bb7e09fe5d6d2e8dc563aa87cf02","tid":906200,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ecb7d79643a943b17851a18d98b3de2f11cf92","tid":906200,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:29:20.000Z","msg":"好似冇人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:30:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80406d836d9619ea27d26d04d1a79c72b44acea","tid":906200,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T19:28:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"098c5527ab49614e774a65eaa287619fbfe85a51","tid":906200,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T19:35:32.000Z","msg":"GF 唔鍾意我打機有女人，成日為依d 野嘈，好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPubg mobile黎"},{"pid":"85c2582c7b02050bb27effcf6edcfd9f0f0ec216","tid":906200,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098c5527ab49614e774a65eaa287619fbfe85a51","tid":906200,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T19:35:32.000Z","msg":"GF 唔鍾意我打機有女人，成日為依d 野嘈，好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPubg mobile黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1